## WHAT HAPPENS NEXT

1. **Acknowledgment:** The Tribunal will acknowledge receipt of your application
2. **Case Management Discussion (CMD):** The Tribunal may convene a CMD to discuss the case
3. **Hearing:** A hearing will be scheduled (usually within 8-12 weeks)
4. **Decision:** The Tribunal will issue a written decision
5. **Eviction:** If granted, you must apply to sheriff officers to enforce the eviction order

